HEADWORD: Swap
<hw>Swap</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Swap</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>Hastily.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Swape</ent>⟦br⟧
